<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home Page</title>
    <style>
     body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      background-color: #f0f4f7;
    }

    header {
      background-color: #081b29; 
      color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 36px;
    }

    ul {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-evenly;
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
      margin: 0;
    }

    nav ul li {
      display: inline;
    }

    nav ul li a {
      color: #fff;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 10px;
      display: block;
    }

    li a:hover {
      background-color: aquamarine;
    }

    .block {
      background-image: url('https://w0.peakpx.com/wallpaper/496/310/HD-wallpaper-%E2%9D%A6-water-fresh-fruits-splashing-thumbnail.jpg') ;
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      height: 500px;
      color: white;
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      text-shadow: 2px 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.7);
    }

    .block h2 {
      font-size: 60px;
      margin: 0;
    }

    section {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 50px;
    }

    section h2 {
      font-size: 50px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    section p {
      font-size: 25px;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }

    .product-showcase {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-around;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
      gap: 20px;
    }

    .product {
      background-color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      border-radius: 10px;
      width: 30%;
    }

    .product img {
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 10px;
    }

    .product h3 {
      margin: 15px 0;
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .benefits {
      background-color: #e0f7fa;
      padding: 50px;
    }

    .benefits h3 {
      font-size: 35px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .benefits ul {
      list-style-type: square;
      font-size: 20px;
      text-align: left;
      margin: 0 auto;
      max-width: 600px;
    }

    .benefits ul li {
        margin:20px;
    }

    footer {
      background-color: #081b29;
      color: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      margin-top: auto;
    }
        </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <h1>Fruit Market</h1>
        <nav>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="#" onclick="showPopup()">Home</a></li>
            <li><a href="about" onclick="showPopup()">About</a></li>
            <li><a href="product" onclick="showPopup()">Products</a></li>
            <li><a href="cart" onclick="showPopup()"> Cart</a></li>
            <li><a href="contact" onclick ="showPopup()">Contact</a></li>
          </ul>
          
        </nav>
    
      </header>
      <section>
        <div class="block">
            <h2>Fresh, Organic & Delicious Fruits</h2>
          </div>
        
          <section class="product-showcase">
            <div class="product">
              <img src="https://images.everydayhealth.com/images/diet-nutrition/apples-101-about-1440x810.jpg?sfvrsn=f86f2644_5" alt="Apple">
              <h3>Fresh Apples</h3>
              <p>Sweet, crisp, and perfect for a healthy snack.</p>
            </div>
        
            <div class="product">
              <img src="https://mana.md/wp-content/uploads/2021/11/banana-1025109_1280-1024x793.jpg" alt="Bananas">
              <h3>Organic Bananas</h3>
              <p>Rich in potassium and great for a quick energy boost.</p>
            </div>
        
            <div class="product">
              <img src="https://media.istockphoto.com/id/1008375528/photo/orange-fruit-with-green-leafs-in-basket-on-grey-wooden-table.jpg?s=612x612&w=0&k=20&c=igWpC0k_kNA853hryjSaew9Jo26Y3SSgM0CMRphAyUQ=" alt="Oranges">
              <h3>Juicy Oranges</h3>
              <p>High in vitamin C, perfect for fresh juice.</p>
            </div>
          </section>
        
          <section class="benefits">
            <h3>Benefits of Fresh Fruit</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Rich in essential vitamins and minerals.</li>
              <li>Boosts the immune system.</li>
              <li>Promotes healthy digestion.</li>
              <li>Helps in weight management.</li>
              <li>Improves overall health and well-being.</li>
            </ul>
          </section>
        
        </section>
      
  <footer>
    <p>&copy; 2024 Fruit Market. All rights reserved.</p>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>